Hindi, ito ay.

386
00:37:04,800 --> 00:37:07,240
Kaya kong kainin ang buong kawali.

387
00:37:08,120 --> 00:37:09,360
Tapos sige. Kumain ng marami.

388
00:37:38,560 --> 00:37:39,680
salamat po

