444
00:43:11,800 --> 00:43:15,000
Malapit na ako sa front door.
Pero wala akong nakikitang tao sa labas.

445
00:43:16,480 --> 00:43:19,760
Ayla, makinig ka sa akin. Mag-ingat.

446
00:43:20,520 --> 00:43:21,360
Okay.

447
00:43:21,440 --> 00:43:23,280
Dahan-dahang lumapit.

448
00:43:23,960 --> 00:43:26,680
Kung may makita ka, sumigaw.

449
00:43:31,040 --> 00:43:32,320
Nasa pintuan ako ngayon.

450
00:43:34,080 --> 00:43:35,400
Manatiling alerto.

451
00:43:36,160 --> 00:43:38,760
Mabagal na kumilos.

452
00:43:42,200 --> 00:43:43,280
Manalo!

453
00:43:45,560 --> 00:43:48,520
Umaga. Nagdala ako ng congee.

454
00:43:57,680 --> 00:43:58,920
pano mo nalaman

455
00:43:59,960 --> 00:44:02,000
Mahilig ako sa congee na may Chinese crullers?

456
00:44:04,800 --> 00:44:08,040
Sabi ko sayo, nasa akin lahat ng info mo.

457
00:44:08,800 --> 00:44:11,520
Hindi pwede. Wala yan sa files.

458
00:44:14,320 --> 00:44:17,320
There's this girl who chattered non-stop
about what she likes to eat

459
00:44:20,000 --> 00:44:24,160
bandang 4 am

460
00:44:29,480 --> 00:44:31,520
Ang lugar na ito ay nagbebenta ng masarap na congee,

461
00:44:32,200 --> 00:44:36,160
